room_title: Escape room "The Auction House Mystery" by Questledge in Springfield (MO)
room_description: Built in 1917, the historic downtown Auction House has seen many interesting items pass through its doors. Quite a few interesting things were found in the basement. One could ruin your entire day...maybe leave you trapped forever... what could it be? Will your team of 4 - 10 players be able to discover the secret and save the building from destruction? You only have one hour... wait... is that the floor rumbling...? Can you solve the mystery and find the missing item before time runs out and you are sunk forever?
